        ": سئل عن معنى الله فقال: استولى على ما دق وجل"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "3. [3/389] al-Kafi: A number of our companions from Ahmad b. Muhammad al-Barqi from al-Qasim b. Yahya from his grandfather al-Hasan b. Rashid from Abi al-Hasan Musa b. Ja’far عليه السلام. He (al-Hasan) said: He (the Imam) was asked about the meaning of Allah so he said: The one who rules over what is lowly and great."
        ]
      }
